<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="heading-xlarge">We can’t tell you which company verified you</h1>
    <p>Security standards mean GOV.UK can’t store your information, so we can’t tell you which company you registered with.</p>
    <p>Look for correspondence from a certified company. Check your:</p>
    <ul class="list-bullet list">
      <li>email inbox for the confirmation email</li>
      <li>spam folder and deleted emails</li>
      <li>texts on your mobile phone</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can try to get your identity verified by a certified company again.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
